Commission to review and level the bilateral trade imbalance
unfavourable to Zambia, the Zambia News Agency ZANA reported.
</P>
<P>
Walubita called on the on-going four-day commission meeting
which started Sunday, to come up with appropriate recommendations
that would enhance a bilateral trade agreement acceptable to both
