services and expanding the cooperation base in the fields of oil
prospection and drilling as well as extending a pipeline for
carrying the Iraqi crude oil to Jordan.
</P>
<P>
They will set up a refining plant in the Jordanian port of
Aqaba.
</P>
<P>
Hourani and his party arrived here last Monday for a week-long
official visit to Iraq. They will leave for home later today.
</P>
