<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 29 (Xinhua) -- At least 20 people were
injured when the Mumbai-New Delhi express train rammed into a
stationary freight train at Chata of Maharashtra State in
southeastern India Monday.
</P>
<P>
